content.rendered:
GEOKC Event Registration Form

About
This event is welcome to all! Download the Event Flyer (PDF) for complete information on this event.

* Please arrive 10-15 minutes before the event begins to purchase tickets. Family members or guests are most welcome to attend.

Price
Price will be $30 including the meal.

Address
Global Expansion of Krishna Community
727 5th Ave. S. #204
Minneapolis, MN 55415

Fill out my online form.
